General Information

An Intensive eye treatment designed to refresh tired looking eyes.

Warnings

To ensure skin compatibility, it is advisable to test a small area of the skin before use. Use the mask immediately after opening to prevent essence from drying out.

Ingredients

Aqua/Water/Eau, Glycerin, Sodium Polyacrylate, Sorbitol, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Cellulose
Gum, Polyacrylic Acid, Octyldodecanol, Kaolin, Charcoal Powder, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Extract,
Sesamum Indicum (Sesame) Seed Extract, Glycine Max (Soybean) Seed Extract, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf
Juice Powder, Allantoin, Aluminum Hydroxide, Aesculus Hippocastanum (Horse Chestnut) Seed Extract,
Ficus Carica (Fig) Fruit/Leaf Extract, Ulmus Davidiana Root Extract, Diospyros Kaki Leaf Extract,
Phenoxyethanol, Retinyl Palmitate, CI 77499, Tocopheryl Acetate, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tartaric Acid,
Disodium EDTA, Caffeine, Butylene Glycol, Volcanic Ash Extract, 1,2-Hexanediol, Limonene, Sodium
Hyaluronate, Linalool, Citronellol, Hydroxycitronellal, Parfum/Fragrance.

Directions

Caffeine energizes the eye area and helps reduce the appearance of dark circles and puffiness. Collagen defends against the signs of aging smoothing fine lines and wrinkles and firming the entire eye area.
